Brooke Hayward https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brooke_Hayward 0 Brooke Hayward (born July 5, 1937) is an American stage, film and television actress. She is the author of Haywire, a best-selling memoir about her family. Brooke_Hayward ( born July_5_,_1937 ) is an_American_stage , film_and_television_actress .
